title: Home Owners, San Francisco, 2000
name: Home Owners, San Francisco, 2000
description: This data summarizes number of home owners by residence by census tract for the San Francisco metropolitan area. The indices are normalized versions of the total and per capita values. For any given census tract, the normalized index is computed as follows: (Value/MaxValue)*100 The source of the data is the 2000 Census Transportation Planning Package (CTPP)from the Bureau of Transportation Statistics.

author.source: Bureau of Transportation Statistics National Transportation Atlas Database
